    <section class="content-grid">
      <article class="panel">
        <h2>Problem</h2>
        <p>The previous site had unclear navigation, inconsistent visual hierarchy, and a booking flow that caused drop-off before checkout.</p>

        <h2>Approach</h2>
        <p>I rebuilt the information architecture around user intent, created a clearer package comparison, and refined trust signals with stronger social proof and photography placement.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Audited booking journey and identified high-friction steps.</li>
          <li>Redesigned key pages for readability and mobile use.</li>
          <li>Implemented cleaner CTA strategy for inquiries and bookings.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Outcome</h2>
        <p>The new site improved discoverability and made booking actions much more direct, especially for mobile visitors planning trips on the go.</p>
